node.text:
Welcome to Mykonos, Greece 🇬🇷 which spot is your favorite, from 1-7? 😍
1. @momentsofgregory in @180mykonos
2. @juliagal_ in @cavotagoomykonos
3. @ftoon.ae in @baosmykonos
4. @ftoon.ae in @kastros_mykonos
5. @ftoon.ae in @negrita.mykonos
6. @juliagal_ in @cavotagoomykonos
7. @ftoon.ae in Mykonos Town
Tag your best travel photos with #travellingthroughtheworld
